#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:2
msgid "IC 引脚检测 2D（Lead 2D，AI）"
msgstr "IC Lead Inspection 2D (AI)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:6
msgid "在引脚阵列上自动生成引脚子框，结合 AI 缺陷检测识别桥接、缺焊、虚焊、少锡等。"
msgstr ""
"Automatically generates per-lead sub-frames across the lead array and "
"combines them with AI defect detection to catch solder bridges, missing "
"solder, cold solder, and insufficient solder."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the tool's"
" parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:14
msgid "**用途**：在引脚阵列上自动生成引脚子框，结合 AI 缺陷检测识别桥接、缺焊、虚焊、少锡等。检测框上的三角箭头指向引脚 *外侧*。"
msgstr ""
"**Purpose**: generate per-lead sub-frames across the lead array and combine "
"them with AI defect detection to catch solder bridges, missing solder, cold "
"solder, and insufficient solder. The triangle marker on the ROI points to "
"the *outside* of the leads."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst
msgid "引脚2D(AI)示意"
msgstr "IC Lead 2D (AI) illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:20
msgid "**参数说明**"
msgstr "**Parameters**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:22
msgid "**引脚数量（Lead Count）**：在 ROI 内自动均分生成对应个数的子 ROI。"
msgstr "**Lead Count**: the ROI is divided into this many equal sub-ROIs."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:23
msgid "**引脚宽度 (mm)（Lead Width）**：匹配实际引脚宽度，使子 ROI 与实体引脚对齐。"
msgstr ""
"**Lead Width (mm)**: matches the physical lead width so each sub-ROI aligns "
"with the corresponding lead."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:24
msgid "**引脚角度（Lead Angle）**：引脚相对 ROI 的方向角。"
msgstr "**Lead Angle**: the lead direction relative to the ROI."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:25
msgid "**引脚阈值（Lead Threshold）**：基于每个引脚子 ROI 的 AI 分数判定缺陷。"
msgstr ""
"**Lead Threshold**: AI-score threshold applied to each per-lead sub-ROI."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:26
msgid "**桥接阈值（Bridge Threshold）**：相邻引脚间连锡（短路）的判定阈值。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge Threshold**: threshold for detecting solder bridges (shorts) "
"between adjacent leads."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:27
msgid ""
"**桥接宽度 (mm)（Bridge Width）/ 间隙宽度 (%)（Gap "
"Width）**：定义相邻引脚间桥接检测带的宽度；可按毫米或按引脚间隙百分比设定，居中裁剪以避免引脚边缘干扰。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge Width (mm) / Gap Width (%)**: define the width of the bridge-"
"detection band between adjacent leads. Configure it in millimeters or as a "
"percentage of the lead gap; the band is centered between the leads to avoid "
"lead-edge interference."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:28
msgid ""
"**引脚忽略列表（Lead Ignore List）/ 桥接忽略列表（Bridge Ignore List）**：选择不参与检测的引脚 / "
"桥接（从左到右编号，注意特征框角度）。"
msgstr ""
"**Lead Ignore List / Bridge Ignore List**: lists of leads or bridges to "
"exclude from inspection (numbered left to right; mind the feature box "
"orientation)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:29
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：显示引脚子框与检测结果。"
msgstr ""
"**Enable Visualization**: shows the per-lead sub-frames and the detection "
"results overlaid on the canvas."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:30
msgid "**使用同步参数（Use sync param）**：开启后，对同一组件下所有同类型引脚特征共用一套参数；关闭后可对单个特征单独调参。"
msgstr ""
"**Use sync param**: when on, every lead feature of this type within the same"
" component shares one parameter set; turn it off to tune a single feature "
"independently."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst
msgid "引脚2D AI检测示意"
msgstr "IC Lead 2D AI inspection illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:37
msgid "**常见问题与提示**"
msgstr "**Common questions and tips**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:41
msgid "**引脚末端误报多**：若元件末端没有红色焊料，关闭 **引脚末端** 子检测。"
msgstr ""
"**Frequent false positives on the lead tip**: if the lead tip has no red "
"solder, turn off the **Lead Tip** sub-check."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:42
msgid "**焊盘检测误报多**：焊盘检测把红色作为有效区域；若元件引脚没有明显焊盘区域，关闭 **焊盘** 子检测。"
msgstr ""
"**Frequent false positives on the pad**: pad inspection treats red as the "
"valid region; if the leads don't expose a clear pad area, turn off the "
"**Pad** sub-check."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/lead_2d.rst:43
msgid "**短引脚定位不准**：使用 **短引脚模式**，整段引脚作为一个检测区域，定位更稳定。"
msgstr ""
"**Short leads are localized poorly**: use **Short-lead mode**, which "
"inspects the whole lead as one region and tracks more reliably."
